  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our school is a good school primary education development project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nepal&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s education system can&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;t offer child friendly school environment to all. Project&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s development problem is that public schools and teachers lack adequate teaching learning methods and infrastructure resulting children dropping out of schools. This project aims to strengthen teacher&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s role in their community and inside the education system, form learning network among teachers, promote child&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s rights and participation in schools and sensitize stakeholders to take responsible role for implementation. Through these activities the objective of this project: Child Friendly School concept is widely accepted and practiced in public schools in the project area. Motivated and skilful teachers and inspiring and safe school environment are available to all the children at the 14 schools in 5 VDCs will be reached.</narrative>
  </description>
